## API Endpoints

### Auth Routes

- `POST /api/auth/register` - Register a new user
- `POST /api/auth/login` - Login a user
- `GET /api/auth/logout` - Logout a user
- `GET /api/auth/me` - Get current logged-in user

### Podcast Routes

- `GET /api/podcasts` - Get all podcasts
- `GET /api/podcasts/:id` - Get podcast by ID
- `POST /api/podcasts` - Create a new podcast
- `PUT /api/podcasts/:id` - Update a podcast by ID
- `DELETE /api/podcasts/:id` - Delete a podcast by ID

### Coaching Session Routes

- `GET /api/coaching-sessions` - Get all coaching sessions
- `POST /api/coaching-sessions` - Book a new coaching session

### Testimonial Routes

- `GET /api/testimonials` - Get all testimonials
- `POST /api/testimonials` - Create a new testimonial

